<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFWhealey2007">Whealey, Alice (2007), <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=JRl1T876naAC" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=JRl1T876naAC" rel="nofollow">"Josephus, Eusebius of Caesarea, and the Testimonium Flavianum"</a>, in Böttrich, Christfried; Herzer, Jens; Reiprich, Torsten, <i>Josephus und das neue Testament</i>, Tübingen: Mohr Siebeck, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/3161493680" class="internal">ISBN 3161493680</a><span class="printonly">, <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=JRl1T876naAC" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=JRl1T876naAC" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?id=JRl1T876naAC</a></span></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Josephus%2C+Eusebius+of+Caesarea%2C+and+the+Testimonium+Flavianum&amp;rft.atitle=Josephus+und+das+neue+Testament&amp;rft.aulast=Whealey&amp;rft.aufirst=Alice&amp;rft.au=Whealey%2C+Alice&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.place=T%C3%BCbingen&amp;rft.pub=Mohr+Siebeck&amp;rft.isbn=3161493680&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DJRl1T876naAC&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Josephus_on_Jesus"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>. Criticizes the thesis that Eusebius of Caesarea fabricated the Testimonium.</li>
<li>Whealey, Alice. "The Testimonium Flavianum in Syriac and Arabic," New Testament Studies 54.4 (2008) pp. 571-590.</li>
<li>Zindler, Frank R. <i>The Jesus The Jews Never Knew, Sepher Toldoth Yeshu and the Quest of the historical Jesus in Jewish Sources</i> (AAP), 2003.</li>
</ul>
